data.title: Databases
data.text:
An international, business-focused newspaper that provides leading news, information, commentary, and analysis. Includes access to all content including newsletters, videos, and podcasts.

Use this link to register for an account on the Wall Street Journal website. Afterwards, you can access your account directly at wsj.com. You can find more detailed instructions about registration in the newspapers guide.

Focusing on the evolution of feminism throughout the nineteenth and twentieth centuries, the Women's Studies Archive provides materials on women's political activism, such as suffrage, birth control, pacifism, civil rights, and socialism, and on women's voices, from female-authored literature to women's periodicals. Trial ends September 27th, 2024.
